public class ForecastStep
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
mreinstadler This class represents one step of forecast (e.g. if the periodicity is hourly, then it represents one full hour) with the weather, events, holidays and the list of ParkingPrediction: for each ParkingPlace one NumericalPrediction
